///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @addtogroup MIDILAR_Examples_LUT_2D
 * @brief Practical examples showcasing 2D lookup table generation and use cases.
 *
 * This group includes examples built on the `LUT2D` base class, illustrating how
 * to implement and interact with 2-dimensional lookup tables for parameterized signal shaping,
 * dynamic waveform control, and morphable transfer functions.
 *
 * These examples are useful for applications where two inputs define the output value —
 * such as phase and shape, velocity and modulation depth, or other multidimensional control signals.
 *
 * All examples are designed with embedded-friendliness and clarity in mind.
 */
